rComments: This was the worst course I ever took in terms of lectures, structure, assignments, help from instructor and overall learning experience. Only good thing was the content but it is horribly taught. The course average was a C. The assignment and final marking is unnecessarily strict and sometimes didn't make sense. AVOID. THIS. COURSE. very bad.
Great class! didn't attend a single lecture but ended up with an 85.

Avoid this professor at all cost! Talking in circles most of the time you won't know what his point is. Lecture slides very disorganized, mostly just throwing some really sophisticated graphs on powerpoint and do not make an effort to explain them. Lots of papers and lack of communications between TAs who grade your paper and the professor.

If you are thinking about taking this course, please treat yourself better and find another one. The slides are horrible with no structured content. The professor cannot even figure out how to make the font consistent throughout all the slides. Lectures are boring and grades are low.
